El 80% de los jugones sencillos es mayor de 30 años
Lo cuentan en <a href="http://blogs.zdnet.com/ITFacts/?p=12121" rel="bookmark" title="Permalink"> 89% of casual gamers are 30+ years old</a> by <a href="http://zdnet.com">ZDNet</a>'s ZDNet Research -- According to Information Solutions Group, 89% of casual gamers are 30 or older, 72% are female, and 53% are married with kids. Nearly half are college graduates.


